Use the standard library
This is how to count_up_to of n:
  Remember that primes is []
  Do this n times:
    Remember that candidate is primes's length
    Increase candidate by 2
    Remember that is_prime is yes
    Remember that divisor is 2
    Do this candidate times:
      When divisor is at most candidate, then:
        When remainder of candidate and divisor is 0, then:
          Remember that is_prime is no
          Leave the loop
        End when
        Increase divisor
      But, if not:
        Leave the loop
      End when
    End do
    When is_prime is yes, then:
      Add primes to candidate
    End when
  End do
  The answer is primes
